1.00	Eric%2C_or%2C_Little_by_Little	Eric, or, Little by Little	Eric, or, Little by Little is the title of a book by Frederic W. Farrar, first edition 1858. It was published by Adam &amp; Charles Black, Edinburgh and London. The book deals with the descent into moral turpitude of a boy at a boarding school.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/96/Eric_little_by_little_cover.jpg/250px-Eric_little_by_little_cover.jpg
